// anastasia's mate 

// a knight and rook team up to trap the opposing king between the side of the board on one side and a friendly piece on the other.

cql()
flipcolor{btm mate
R -> k
_ <- k == 4


square all x in _ <- k
       (R -> x) or (N -> x)}


